<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٨٣ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6542">نَصْرُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4599">أَبِي، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5202">قُرَّةَ بْنِ خَالِدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«هَذَا جَبَلٌ يُحِبُّنَا وَنُحِبُّهُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>